org.jscsi.target.connection.phase
Class TargetPhase

java.lang.Object
  org.jscsi.target.connection.phase.TargetPhase
Direct Known Subclasses:
TargetFullFeaturePhase, TargetLoginPhase
public abstract class TargetPhase
extends Object

Instances of this class represent a connection's phase (see TargetConnection for a description of the relationship between stages, phases, connections, and sessions).

To start a phase, one of the execute methods must be called, which one is sub-class-specific.

Author:
Andreas Ergenzinger
